  <brief_title>A Double-blind Study to Investigate Efficacy, Safety and Tolerability of BAY 1142524 in Patients After Acute Myocardial Infarction With Left-ventricular Dysfunction</brief_title>
  <acronym>CHIARA MIA 2</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Multicenter Study to Assess the Safety and Efficacy of a 6 Month Oral Treatment With the Chymase Inhibitor BAY 1142524 at a Dose of 25 mg BID in Comparison to Placebo on Top of Standard of Care in Patients With Reduced Left-ventricular Ejection Fraction (LVEF≤ 45%) After Acute Myocardial Infarction</official_title>
